Prerequisites
=============

LunarDate requires GLib-2.32.x libraries.

Simple install procedure
========================

  $ tar -zxf lunar-date-@PACKAGE_VERSION@.tar.gz              # unpack the sources
  $ cd lunar-date-@PACKAGE_VERSION@                           # change to the toplevel directory
  $ ./configure --prefix=/usr [--enable-gtk-doc --enable-vala-bindings ]  # run the `configure' script
  $ make                                        # build lunar-date
  [ Become root if necessary ]
  $ sudo make install                           # install lunar-date

